<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>BAWIPA CUNGAH I LAWM TUAH U CH360</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Lungthin a dingmi vialte hna, Jesuh sinah lunglawm tuah u, Bawi Jesuh
 a thim vialte hna, Ngaihchiat thinphannak kha hlaw tuah.

[C1]
   Lawm tuah, (Lawmtuah, Jesuh sin lawm) lawm tuah (Lawm tuah), Jesuh
   sinah lunglawm tuah u, Lawmtuah (Jesu sin lawm tuah) lawm tuah (lawm
   tuah) Jesuh sinah lunglawm tuah u.

[V2]
 Bawi Jesuh kha lawm cio tuah u, Van le vawlei zong kha a uk; A kut
 chung ummi kan si i, A nunnak in a kan tlanh cang.

[C2]
   Lawm tuah, (Lawmtuah, Jesuh sin lawm) lawm tuah (Lawm tuah), Jesuh
   sinah lunglawm tuah u, Lawmtuah (Jesu sin lawm tuah) lawm tuah (lawm
   tuah) Jesuh sinah lunglawm tuah u.

[V3]
 Bawipa a ralkap vialte hna, Rul-hreu nih tei deng hmanh sehlaw, Jesuh
 a zulmi vialte kha Ral vialte nakin an thawng deuh.

[C3]
   Lawm tuah, (Lawmtuah, Jesuh sin lawm) lawm tuah (Lawm tuah), Jesuh
   sinah lunglawm tuah u, Lawmtuah (Jesu sin lawm tuah) lawm tuah (lawm
   tuah) Jesuh sinah lunglawm tuah u.

[V4]
 Chun caan ah khuamui hmanhsehlaw, Khuamui nih van phen hmanhsehlaw, Na
 thlarau tihnak a um lo, Nunnak a dongh tiangin zum tuah.

[C4]
   Lawm tuah, (Lawmtuah, Jesuh sin lawm) lawm tuah (Lawm tuah), Jesuh
   sinah lunglawm tuah u, Lawmtuah (Jesu sin lawm tuah) lawm tuah (lawm
   tuah) Jesuh sinah lunglawm tuah u.</lyrics>
<key>Bb</key>
<hymn_number>360</hymn_number>
</song>